Package: absCopyNumber
Type: Package
Title: Tumor Purity, Ploidy and Absolute Copy Number Estimation
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: c(person("Shixiang", "Wang", email = "w_shixiang@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9855-7357")),
            person("Bao", "Lei", email = "lebao@ucsd.edu", role="aut")) 
Maintainer: Shixiang Wang <w_shixiang@163.com>
URL: https://github.com/ShixiangWang/absCopyNumber
BugReports: https://github.com/ShixiangWang/absCopyNumber/issues
Description: Easy and comprehensive R toolbox for estimating tumor purity, ploidy and absolute copy numbers 
             from NGS (WGS, WES, Target Sequencing) and Microarray (SNP, aCGH etc.) data, 
             based on a copy-number-based ratio estimator and a optional SNV-frequency-based estimator.
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
Imports: graphics, stats, utils, methods, readr, data.table
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    prettydoc,
    R.utils
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
